OL,3,CPaedophile who abused teenager more
OL,4,Cthan 20 years ago jailed
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 7 May, Jones, of King
OL,7,FGeorge Road, Colchester, Essex, was
OL,8,Fsentenced to three and a half years
OL,9,Fbehind bars, made to sign the Sex
OL,10,FOffender's Register for life and given
OL,11,Fa Sexual Harm Prevention Order (SHPO)
OL,12,Fand restraining order.
OL,14,Fpraised the bravery of his victim, and
OL,15,Fsaid 'no matter how much time has
OL,16,Fpassed, we're here for you.'
