OL,6,FThe officer leading the investigation
OL,7,Ffor Northumbria Police, Detective
OL,8,FConstable Andrea Nixon, said: "The
OL,9,Foutcome of this case sends a clear
OL,10,Fmessage ` it's never too late to seek
OL,11,Fjustice, and it is possible to hold
OL,12,Fyour abuser to account years, even
OL,13,Fdecades, after the crimes have been
OL,14,Fcommitted."
OL,16,F"It also should be taken as a clear
OL,17,Fwarning to anyone who thinks they've
OL,18,Fgotten away with committing non-recent
OL,19,Fabuse ` we can and will find you, and
OL,20,Fyour crimes will be pursued regardless
OL,21,Fof how much time has passed."
